SO!!! I heard you want to Eddie???????
Well you better sign up tonight for one of my add on classes at Cookie con Orlando!
•
In this class we will have not one, but TWO Eddie’s to use. We will not only be hands on making these cookies but also be learning where and how to find images to match your sets so you can better use Eddie in the future. We will find clipart to MAKE a cookie cutter (🤞🏼hoping to bring a 3D printer to print while we are in class) & then how to print right on the cutter with Eddie! This class is jammed pack for the everyday cookier who is ready to step up their game with Eddie! We will be using Swift to print on the cookies- which is for Mac computers
•
•
When I say this is a Mac class I just mean I’m not teaching the program that goes with PC for Eddie use. We will be using
• Swift 
• Canva Pro @canva 
• cookiecad.com @cookie.cad 
• silhouette studio designer edition @silhouette.inc 
• possibly procreate @procreate 
But you don’t need these programs to take this class- you can just be learning and taking notes
